win32_timeout
last revised 10.07.2017

a couple of Win32 console applications that perform an action after a specific
amount of time. the source code is ANSI C compatible.

shutdown_timeout:
	shuts down the system after N minutes. gives a 30 second countdown.

alarm_timeout:
	plays alarm_timeout.wav on a loop after N minutes.

ping_timeout:
	play a sound and show a message box after succeeding to ICMP echo an
	IPV4 address.

use Mingw and GNU Make to build:
	cd <source_path>
	make
